    "description": "<br><br>《地牢翻新模拟器》提供了一次独特的冒险，让您穿上“被诅咒的哥布林”清洁工和翻新工的鞋子，置身于一个中世纪灵感的世界中。在这款单人模拟游戏中，您将探索、清理并重生引人入胜的环境，每个环境都带有一系列基于物理的挑战和隐藏的任务。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>像地精一样清理</strong></h2>探索充满污垢、血液和其他奇特物质的地牢，前往曾经宁静统治的宏伟餐厅，如今已经结束。凭借“奥术吸尘器”，您将处理即使是最混乱的工作。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222020/extras/6bc8cb5270e78879771ab19578bb4bf7.poster.avif?t=1760614914\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222020/extras/6bc8cb5270e78879771ab19578bb4bf7.webm?t=1760614914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222020/extras/6bc8cb5270e78879771ab19578bb4bf7.mp4?t=1760614914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一切都是物理学</strong></h2>与几乎每个物体互动，为您提供创造性的自由，让您为这些迷人的中世纪环境注入新的生命。瞄准、投掷、吸尘和拖把，通过这些方式将它们转变成您独特的愿景。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222020/extras/27950315ad57243b7f04dfcfa2fe9fef.poster.avif?t=1760614914\" width=616 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222020/extras/27950315ad57243b7f04dfcfa2fe9fef.webm?t=1760614914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222020/extras/27950315ad57243b7f04dfcfa2fe9fef.mp4?t=1760614914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>揭开谜团</strong></h2>发现这些多样空间中的隐藏秘密，参与身临其境的“基于物理学的任务”解锁新关卡，并揭示其中隐藏的引人入胜的故事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222020/extras/91ac7dbc1140df7340a3f72258d28b68.poster.avif?t=1760614914\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222020/extras/91ac7dbc1140df7340a3f72258d28b68.webm?t=1760614914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2222020/extras/91ac7dbc1140df7340a3f72258d28b68.mp4?t=1760614914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
